 I sad, to koliko si jak i koliko si izdržljiv

556
00:32:08,660 --> 00:32:11,540
 se može promatrati iz raznih kuteva.

557
00:32:11,540 --> 00:32:14,760
 To koliko si jak je jedna stvar sa 25 godina,

558
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:16,960
 druga stvar sa 75 godina,

559
00:32:16,960 --> 00:32:19,140
 ali i sa 75 godina bi trebalo imati

560
00:32:19,140 --> 00:32:20,440
 odgovarajući stisak šake,

561
00:32:20,440 --> 00:32:22,480
 koji se pokazuje da je u visokoj korelaciji

562
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:23,660
 sa dugovječnosti.

563
00:32:23,660 --> 00:32:24,580
 Dakle, stisak šake.

564
00:32:24,580 --> 00:32:25,980
 To je neka bazična jakost.

565
00:32:25,980 --> 00:32:27,160
 Kroz koje pokrete?

566
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,040
 Sad je sljedeće pitanje.

567
00:32:28,040 --> 00:32:28,920
 Kroz koje pokrete?

568
00:32:28,920 --> 00:32:30,480
 Kroz jednostavne pokrete.

569
00:32:30,580 --> 00:32:31,800
 Samo ću ti reći tri pokreta.

570
00:32:31,800 --> 00:32:33,480
 Neka vrsta potiska.

571
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:35,600
 Dakle, to može biti sklek.

572
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:37,960
 Od skleka do rada sa utezima

573
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:39,620
 do skleka na jednoj ruci

574
00:32:39,620 --> 00:32:41,120
 koji bi trebali svi mi raditi.

575
00:32:41,120 --> 00:32:43,680
 Što zvuči sad čudno i ono...

576
00:32:43,680 --> 00:32:44,660
 Ne znam, pa što vrtim.

577
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:46,100
 Znam, ja mogu.

578
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:47,940
 Naravno da može, pa svi možemo.

579
00:32:47,940 --> 00:32:49,760
 A ne mora biti na podu.

580
00:32:49,760 --> 00:32:51,520
 Možeš ti sa jednom rukom?

581
00:32:51,520 --> 00:32:53,100
 Sklek, da.

582
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:55,580
 Oh, povisi koji dan.

583
00:32:55,580 --> 00:32:57,220
 A može svaki dan.

584
00:32:57,220 --> 00:32:58,920
 I svatko od nas može svaki dan.

585
00:32:58,920 --> 00:33:00,420
 Jer nisam rekao da mora biti na podu.

586
00:33:00,580 --> 00:33:03,680
 A, o, kako smo se zavarali.

587
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:05,140
 Slušam, slušam.

588
00:33:05,140 --> 00:33:06,560
 Ali kad je dlan na zidu

589
00:33:06,560 --> 00:33:07,760
 i radiš sklek na jednoj ruci

590
00:33:07,760 --> 00:33:09,680
 usput moraš aktivira stabilizatore trupa,

591
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:10,120
 na primjer.

592
00:33:10,120 --> 00:33:12,400
 Koji spavaju dok sjediš, na primjer.

593
00:33:12,400 --> 00:33:15,220
 Isto tako sam vidio puno jakih ljudi

594
00:33:15,220 --> 00:33:16,860
 koji u vježbi bench press

595
00:33:16,860 --> 00:33:17,800
 guraju puno kila.

596
00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:18,440
 Što je super.

597
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:20,180
 Ali daš im da rade sklek na jednoj ruci

598
00:33:20,180 --> 00:33:20,780
 ne na podu,

599
00:33:20,780 --> 00:33:21,980
 nego ruka na stolu,

600
00:33:21,980 --> 00:33:22,740
 noge na podu.

601
00:33:23,180 --> 00:33:23,880
 jer nije im lako.

602
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:24,920
 Pa čekaj malo,

603
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:25,840
 jesi li onda zaista

604
00:33:25,840 --> 00:33:27,380
 životno jak

605
00:33:27,380 --> 00:33:28,920
 ili si samo jak

606
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:30,060
 kad ležiš na leđima

607
00:33:30,060 --> 00:33:31,140
 i guraš šipku.

608
00:33:31,140 --> 00:33:33,920
 Što ti je važnije

609
00:33:33,920 --> 00:33:34,660
 za dugo vječnost?

610
00:33:34,660 --> 00:33:35,940
 Pa vjerojatno da si životno jak.

611
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:38,180
 Da si sposoban kontrolirati svoje tijelo

612
00:33:38,180 --> 00:33:38,720
 u uvjetima

613
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:40,980
 blage nestabilnosti.

614
00:33:41,360 --> 00:33:41,640
 Tako da,

615
00:33:41,640 --> 00:33:42,400
 naravno,

616
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:43,540
 super je i bench press,

617
00:33:43,540 --> 00:33:44,360
 da se razumijemo.

618
00:33:44,360 --> 00:33:46,180
 Super je i stražni čučanj

619
00:33:46,180 --> 00:33:46,760
 kao vježba,

620
00:33:46,760 --> 00:33:48,020
 ali čučanj kao pokret

621
00:33:48,020 --> 00:33:49,320
 je važniji od vježbe

622
00:33:49,320 --> 00:33:50,160
 stražni čučanj.

623
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:51,320
 Dakle, čučanj kao pokret

624
00:33:51,320 --> 00:33:52,300
 da mogu svojim tijelom

625
00:33:52,300 --> 00:33:52,880
 baratati

626
00:33:52,880 --> 00:33:54,980
 kroz 25 čučnjeva

627
00:33:54,980 --> 00:33:56,460
 u starijoj životnoj dobi.

628
00:33:56,460 --> 00:33:57,520
 Pa to je fenomenalna stvar.

629
00:33:57,520 --> 00:33:58,640
 Tako da,

630
00:33:58,640 --> 00:34:00,360
 to je taj živčano-mišični segment

631
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:01,060
 koji se odnosi

632
00:34:01,060 --> 00:34:02,000
 na to prije svega

633
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:02,820
 koliko sam jak.

634
00:34:02,820 --> 00:34:04,460
 Ali i ta jakost

635
00:34:04,460 --> 00:34:05,120
 se može raditi

636
00:34:05,120 --> 00:34:06,220
 na intenzivnije načine.

637
00:34:06,220 --> 00:34:08,400
 Jer sad kad kažem riječ

638
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:09,880
 eksplozivnost zvuči,

639
00:34:09,880 --> 00:34:10,260
 čekaj,

640
00:34:10,260 --> 00:34:11,660
 to samo rade sportaši.

641
00:34:11,660 --> 00:34:12,060
 Pa ne.

642
00:34:12,060 --> 00:34:13,840
 Za osobu u stariju životnoj dobi

643
00:34:13,840 --> 00:34:15,400
 je super,

644
00:34:15,400 --> 00:34:16,240
 pa da bi spriječio

645
00:34:16,240 --> 00:34:17,100
 potencijalni pad,

646
00:34:17,100 --> 00:34:18,920
 je super ako može

647
00:34:18,920 --> 00:34:19,960
 kontrolirati svoje tijelo

648
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:20,960
 iz neke veće brzine.

649
00:34:20,960 --> 00:34:21,460
 Naprimjer,

650
00:34:21,460 --> 00:34:23,020
 uđi u brzi čučanj

651
00:34:23,020 --> 00:34:23,680
 i zaustavi se

652
00:34:23,680 --> 00:34:24,840
 u brzom čučnju.

653
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:26,300
 Pa to je za osobu u stariju životnoj dobi

654
00:34:26,300 --> 00:34:27,840
 odličan trening eksplozivnosti.

655
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:30,020
 Kao što je za tu istu osobu

656
00:34:30,020 --> 00:34:30,980
 hodanje,

657
00:34:31,360 --> 00:34:32,060
 brzo hodanje

658
00:34:32,060 --> 00:34:33,280
 ili malo brži hod,

659
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:35,040
 recimo na 6 km na sat,

660
00:34:35,040 --> 00:34:36,040
 to je za nju

661
00:34:36,040 --> 00:34:37,720
 zona VO2 max.

662
00:34:37,720 --> 00:34:38,200
 Super.

663
00:34:38,200 --> 00:34:39,880
 Kao što je to

664
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,760
 ta ista zona

665
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:42,120
 za osobu u 25 godina

666
00:34:42,120 --> 00:34:43,220
 možda 12 km

667
00:34:43,220 --> 00:34:44,420
 ili 15 km na sat,

668
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:46,200
 ovisi u kakvoj formi.

669
00:34:46,200 --> 00:34:48,120
 Ali važno je

670
00:34:48,120 --> 00:34:48,940
 biti dovoljno jak,

671
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:50,080
 ne samo jak,

672
00:34:50,080 --> 00:34:51,460
 nego kontrolirati svoje tijelo

673
00:34:51,460 --> 00:34:54,240
 čak pri malo većim brzinama.

674
00:34:54,240 --> 00:34:55,940
 Što opet zvuči kao nešto

675
00:34:55,940 --> 00:34:56,640
 jako teško,

676
00:34:56,640 --> 00:34:57,060
 ali nije.

677
00:34:57,060 --> 00:34:58,320
 Dakle, poruka.

678
00:34:58,320 --> 00:35:00,080
 Skleknaj na ruci nije ništa strašno,

679
00:35:01,200 --> 00:35:02,200
 jer ti nisam opisao

680
00:35:02,200 --> 00:35:02,940
 do kraja vježbu.

681
00:35:02,940 --> 00:35:04,200
 Ne mora biti na podu,

682
00:35:04,200 --> 00:35:05,120
 neka bude na stolu

683
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:05,480
 i evo,

684
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:07,140
 to je test za sve naše gledatelje.

685
00:35:07,140 --> 00:35:08,880
 Ruka na stolu,

686
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:09,580
 noge na podu.

687
00:35:09,580 --> 00:35:10,620
 Da vidimo koliko nisko

688
00:35:10,620 --> 00:35:11,720
 možeš doći

689
00:35:11,720 --> 00:35:12,420
 na jednoj ruci.

690
00:35:12,420 --> 00:35:13,520
 Ako ti je pre teško,

691
00:35:13,520 --> 00:35:14,700
 kreni sa zidom

692
00:35:14,700 --> 00:35:16,300
 i to dlano visini ramena.

693
00:35:16,300 --> 00:35:17,600
 Pa za godinu dana

694
00:35:17,600 --> 00:35:18,440
 dođi do dlana

695
00:35:18,440 --> 00:35:19,800
 na stolu.

696
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:20,740
 To je fenomenalna naprava.

697
00:35:20,740 --> 00:35:22,340
 onda možemo i na podu.

698
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:22,940
 O tom podu.

699
00:35:22,940 --> 00:35:23,900
 Ko može na podu,

700
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:25,160
 taj možda i ne mora to raditi.

701
00:35:25,160 --> 00:35:26,140
 Ajde, javite nam se,

702
00:35:26,140 --> 00:35:26,820
 svi molim vas,

703
00:35:26,820 --> 00:35:27,520
 u komentare

704
00:35:27,520 --> 00:35:28,620
 koji možete na podu,

705
00:35:28,620 --> 00:35:30,140
 a za sve nas ostalo

706
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:31,200
 krenit ćemo od zida.

707
00:35:31,200 --> 00:35:32,640
 bit će i koji mogu na podu.

708
00:35:32,640 --> 00:35:33,520
 Sigurno.

709
00:35:33,520 --> 00:35:36,280
 Jakost i izdržljivost.

710
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:36,600
 Tako je.

711
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:37,480
 Sad ta izdržljivost

712
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:38,740
 opet se gradira.

713
00:35:38,740 --> 00:35:40,800
 Za osobu koja je možda

714
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:41,920
 mlađe životne dobi

715
00:35:41,920 --> 00:35:43,240
 je to nešto drugo.

716
00:35:43,240 --> 00:35:43,940
 Ali ono što je bitno

717
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:45,040
 da provedeš vrijeme,

718
00:35:45,040 --> 00:35:45,560
 rekao sam mu,

719
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:46,180
 nisko intenzivno.

720
00:35:46,180 --> 00:35:47,480
 Kakav je to nisko intenzivni trening?

721
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,020
 Pa to je recimo

722
00:35:48,020 --> 00:35:49,920
 da možeš skoro normalno pjevat

723
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,440
 i lagano trčat

724
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,540
 ili biciklirat.

725
00:35:52,540 --> 00:35:53,380
 To ti je zona dva,

726
00:35:53,380 --> 00:35:54,460
 popularna zona dva

727
00:35:54,460 --> 00:35:56,820
 o kojoj ste vjerojatno čuli puno.

728
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:59,100
 Zona dva je za većinu ljudi

729
00:35:59,100 --> 00:36:01,040
 najlakši mogući jogging.

730
00:36:01,040 --> 00:36:03,360
 Ne moraš biti pogačar

731
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,600
 najbolji biciklist

732
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:05,460
 kojim je zona dva

733
00:36:05,460 --> 00:36:08,340
 kad vrti na 320 wati bicikl.

734
00:36:08,340 --> 00:36:09,580
 A obična osoba

735
00:36:09,580 --> 00:36:10,840
 kad vrti na 150 wati

736
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:11,340
 je u šoku.

737
00:36:11,340 --> 00:36:14,040
 Dakle, on je na 320 wati

738
00:36:14,040 --> 00:36:15,500
 i 4 sata provede u toj zoni.

739
00:36:15,500 --> 00:36:17,300
 Dakle, zona dva je nešto

740
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:19,400
 je zona u kojoj možeš dugo biti.

741
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,900
 I ne trošite.

742
00:36:20,900 --> 00:36:22,080
 Za moje sportaše,

743
00:36:22,080 --> 00:36:23,140
 za moje neke igrače

744
00:36:23,140 --> 00:36:25,740
 zona dva je 12 ili 13 km na sat.

745
00:36:25,740 --> 00:36:26,680
 To je njima zona dva.

746
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:28,040
 Što je fenomenalno.

747
00:36:28,040 --> 00:36:29,180
 Ali naravno,

748
00:36:29,180 --> 00:36:32,140
 civilu je to možda ubrzani hod.

749
00:36:32,140 --> 00:36:33,800
 Što je isto tako

750
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:34,580
 dosta dobra stvar.

751
00:36:34,580 --> 00:36:35,480
 Da ne ulazimo sad

752
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,400
 koliko je to laktata,

753
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,060
 to sad nije bitno.

754
00:36:37,060 --> 00:36:37,780
 Ali da možeš skoro

755
00:36:37,780 --> 00:36:38,460
 normalno pjevat

756
00:36:38,460 --> 00:36:39,820
 i time se baviti.

757
00:36:39,820 --> 00:36:40,640
 Čime se baviš.

758
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:41,840
 Ako više ne možeš

759
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,420
 normalno pjevat,

760
00:36:42,420 --> 00:36:43,140
 ali i dalje pričaš

761
00:36:43,140 --> 00:36:43,760
 u rečenicama,

762
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:45,360
 onda si i dalje

763
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:46,220
 u aerobnoj zoni,

764
00:36:46,220 --> 00:36:48,460
 ali si već u malo višoj

765
00:36:48,460 --> 00:36:49,340
 aerobnoj zoni.

766
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:50,580
 I isto tako bilo bi dobro

767
00:36:50,580 --> 00:36:51,740
 jednom ili dva puta tjedno

768
00:36:51,740 --> 00:36:52,720
 provesti neko vrijeme

769
00:36:52,720 --> 00:36:53,380
 u toj zoni.

770
00:36:53,380 --> 00:36:55,100
 Preporuke koje su

771
00:36:55,100 --> 00:36:56,180
 preporuke najvećih

772
00:36:56,180 --> 00:36:57,100
 svjetskih zdravstvenih

773
00:36:57,100 --> 00:36:58,040
 organizacija su

774
00:36:58,040 --> 00:37:00,280
 da si tjelesno aktivan

775
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:01,520
 i čak da tjelesno vježbaš

776
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:02,920
 oko 150 minuta tjedno.

777
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:05,120
 Dakle, pet puta po 30 minuta

778
00:37:05,120 --> 00:37:07,020
 neke vrste aerobne aktivnosti

779
00:37:07,020 --> 00:37:08,500
 koja ne mora biti čak čisto aerobna,

780
00:37:08,500 --> 00:37:09,980
 može biti malo intenzivniji od toga.

781
00:37:09,980 --> 00:37:12,160
 Dakle, neke niske, srednje

782
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:12,880
 pa do visoke,

783
00:37:12,880 --> 00:37:15,080
 visoko intenzivne tjelesne aktivnosti

784
00:37:15,080 --> 00:37:15,800
 odnosno vježbanja.

785
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:17,240
 To su neke preporuke.

786
00:37:17,240 --> 00:37:18,300
 Što može zvući puno,

787
00:37:18,300 --> 00:37:19,840
 pet puta tjedno po 30 minuta,

788
00:37:19,940 --> 00:37:20,880
 ne mora biti možda toliko.

789
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:22,200
 Ali jednom tjedno

790
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:23,160
 ili dva puta tjedno

791
00:37:23,160 --> 00:37:24,800
 digni frekvenciju srca

792
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:26,940
 u zonu da ti je blago neugodno

793
00:37:26,940 --> 00:37:28,400
 ili neudobno, bolje reći.

794
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:30,240
 U zonu koja je

795
00:37:30,240 --> 00:37:31,700
 van zone konfora

796
00:37:31,700 --> 00:37:32,500
 i gdje se osjećaš

797
00:37:32,500 --> 00:37:34,000
 da ti je zaista intenzivno.

798
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,140
 Jednom ili dva puta tjedno.

799
00:37:35,140 --> 00:37:35,720
 Koliko dugo?

800
00:37:35,720 --> 00:37:38,520
 Pa ako si osoba neke srednje dobi

801
00:37:38,520 --> 00:37:41,420
 ili tamo iza one gospodine.

802
00:37:41,420 --> 00:37:42,720
 Iza mene je bila osoba srednje.

803
00:37:42,720 --> 00:37:45,140
 Ili mlađe,

804
00:37:45,140 --> 00:37:46,580
 onda je to jednom ili dva puta tjedno

805
00:37:46,580 --> 00:37:48,120
 po recimo 10-15 minuta

806
00:37:48,120 --> 00:37:50,300
 visoko intenzivne aktivnosti.

807
00:37:50,300 --> 00:37:52,020
 To bi bila neka zona iznad.

808
00:37:52,020 --> 00:37:52,880
 Iznad, naravno.

809
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:54,620
 Zona dva je nešto što bi svaki dan

810
00:37:54,620 --> 00:37:55,120
 trebali imati.

811
00:37:55,120 --> 00:37:55,780
 To je higijena.

812
00:37:55,780 --> 00:37:57,840
 A onda jednom ili dva puta tjedno

813
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,440
 da ulaziš u zone 4 ili 5

814
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:01,360
 da malo pređeš na nerobni prag.

815
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,320
 A to znači da već

816
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,160
 ne možeš pričati

817
00:38:03,160 --> 00:38:04,180
 u normalnim rečenicama,

818
00:38:04,180 --> 00:38:06,600
 ne možeš bez da se o to osjeti

819
00:38:06,600 --> 00:38:08,600
 po pitanju tvoje frekvencije disanja.

820
00:38:08,600 --> 00:38:09,680
 Da kad preko telefona

821
00:38:09,680 --> 00:38:10,240
 pričaš nekim

822
00:38:10,240 --> 00:38:11,240
 da o taj neko zaista

823
00:38:11,240 --> 00:38:12,940
 vidi da ti ozbiljno treniraš.

824
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:14,000
 Ova zona dva je

825
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:15,640
 da netko nije siguran

826
00:38:15,640 --> 00:38:16,780
 jesi li ti u treningu

827
00:38:16,780 --> 00:38:17,240
 ili nisi.

828
00:38:17,240 --> 00:38:20,360
 I da pričaš preko telefona.

829
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:21,460
 I pričaš preko telefona

830
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:22,700
 je tamman si se izviko

831
00:38:22,700 --> 00:38:23,200
 na djecu.

832
00:38:23,200 --> 00:38:25,000
 Imaš malo povišen puls

833
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:26,300
 i izvučiš kod da si zapravo

834
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:27,640
 i šume došla sa zone 2.

835
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:28,280
 Recimo da.

836
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:31,420
 Dakle, sve što trebamo je zapravo

837
00:38:31,420 --> 00:38:33,200
 pokušat pjevat

838
00:38:33,200 --> 00:38:34,880
 dok šetamo intenzivnije

839
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:35,920
 malo po kvartu,

840
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:37,420
 po ulici, po naselju.

841
00:38:37,420 --> 00:38:40,240
 To raditi minimalno 30 minuta

842
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:40,960
 svaki dan

843
00:38:40,960 --> 00:38:43,540
 ukoliko imamo priliku.

844
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:45,640
 To bi bilo zapravo optimalno.

845
00:38:45,640 --> 00:38:46,780
 Ajmo reći.

846
00:38:46,780 --> 00:38:47,880
 I dva puta tjedno

847
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,980
 dovese u zonu iznad toga

848
00:38:49,980 --> 00:38:51,340
 gdje što s godinama

849
00:38:51,340 --> 00:38:52,580
 bi trebali malo produljiti

850
00:38:52,580 --> 00:38:53,500
 trajanje te zone

851
00:38:53,500 --> 00:38:54,660
 ako sam te dobro shvatila.

852
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:56,620
 Pa da, trebali bi produljiti

853
00:38:56,620 --> 00:38:58,160
 ovo zonu, zonu 2 bi trebalo.

854
00:38:58,160 --> 00:39:00,540
 Mislim, zona 2 je svima potrebna.

855
00:39:00,540 --> 00:39:02,100
 Tako da, ovo pjevanje je da.

856
00:39:02,100 --> 00:39:03,720
 Ako će vas neko čudno gledat

857
00:39:03,720 --> 00:39:04,660
 staviti slušalice,

858
00:39:04,660 --> 00:39:06,920
 pa ćeš gledat kao da je to normalno.

859
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:07,680
 Pa će vas malo manje, manje da.

860
00:39:07,680 --> 00:39:09,460
 To ono kad glaši neko priča sam sa sobom

861
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:10,540
 odmah glaši ili ima slušalice.

862
00:39:10,540 --> 00:39:12,660
 Samo tako je, stavi slušalicu i sve u reći.

863
00:39:12,660 --> 00:39:13,600
 I sve, i sve, ok.

864
00:39:13,600 --> 00:39:16,360
 Možeš maskirati svoje demone u glavi

865
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:18,140
 koji su se pojavili u tom trenutku.

866
00:39:18,140 --> 00:39:21,800
 Postoji li ipak neko vrijeme

867
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:24,120
 kad je kasno započet sa svim tim stvarima?

868
00:39:24,120 --> 00:39:27,680
 Da li ono kao, evo, imam sad 85 godina,

869
00:39:27,680 --> 00:39:30,120
 možda stvarno bi bilo onda zdravije nastave

870
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:31,240
 živjeti kako si je živio,

871
00:39:31,240 --> 00:39:32,760
 nego iću nekakav stres

872
00:39:32,760 --> 00:39:35,240
 po pitanju uvođenja nekakve tjelesne aktivnosti?

873
00:39:35,980 --> 00:39:37,220
 Pa da, opet se vraćamo na ono

874
00:39:37,220 --> 00:39:41,220
 za koliko ocjena ću dići to što trebam dići i popraviti.

875
00:39:41,220 --> 00:39:43,860
 Za jednu ocjenu bi svatko mogao.

876
00:39:43,860 --> 00:39:47,680
 Tako da popraviti tjelesnu aktivnosti sa 85 godina

877
00:39:47,680 --> 00:39:48,940
 pa bilo bi korisno,

878
00:39:48,940 --> 00:39:52,660
 ali to je poprava koja nije toliko značajna

879
00:39:52,660 --> 00:39:56,580
 i toliko velika, ali i dalje može biti dobra pomoć.

880
00:39:56,580 --> 00:39:58,860
 Naravno, treba uzvati obzir i zdravstveni status

881
00:39:58,860 --> 00:40:00,940
 i sve ono što možda ta osoba ima

882
00:40:00,940 --> 00:40:04,040
 kao potencijalne probleme ili dijagnoze

883
00:40:04,040 --> 00:40:05,940
 i onda tome prilagoditi tjelesno vježbanje.

884
00:40:05,980 --> 00:40:06,680
 Definitivno.

885
00:40:06,680 --> 00:40:10,720
 Ali ono što je sigurno je da za kronične nezarazne bolesti

886
00:40:10,720 --> 00:40:14,320
 tjelesno vježbanje i tjelesna aktivnost može zaista pomoći.

887
00:40:14,320 --> 00:40:17,280
 Jer to je na kraju krajeva i jedan od faktora rizika,

888
00:40:17,280 --> 00:40:20,580
 a samim tjelesnim vježbanjem rješavaš neke druge faktore rizika

889
00:40:20,580 --> 00:40:23,560
 za pojavljivanje kroničnih nezaraznih bolesti.

890
00:40:23,560 --> 00:40:26,220
 Najčešće su pretilost, diabetes, hipertenzija.

891
00:40:26,220 --> 00:40:28,700
 To je pošast današnjeg doba.

892
00:40:28,700 --> 00:40:31,280
 A njih se može ublažiti definitivno

893
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:33,460
 i tjelesnim vježbanjem

894
00:40:33,460 --> 00:40:36,740
 uz sve druge zahvate u životnom stilu.

895
00:40:36,740 --> 00:40:38,400
 Danas je medicina životnog stila

896
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:40,660
 legitimni dio medicine.

897
00:40:40,660 --> 00:40:43,260
 Lifestyle medicine je svjetski pokret.

898
00:40:43,260 --> 00:40:44,640
 U Hrvatskoj postoji udruga

899
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:46,200
 za medicinu životnog stila,

900
00:40:46,200 --> 00:40:47,820
 koja je evo sad prije par dana su imali

901
00:40:47,820 --> 00:40:49,780
 kongres u Splitu,

902
00:40:49,780 --> 00:40:52,080
 jako uspješan kongres, svjetski kongres,

903
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:53,580
 koji se događa u Hrvatskoj,

904
00:40:53,580 --> 00:40:55,920
 sa temom medicine životnog stila.

905
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:57,940
 A sve ovo ćemo pričamo danas.

906
00:40:57,940 --> 00:40:59,540
 Ti i ja su u stvari segmenti

907
00:40:59,540 --> 00:41:00,940
 medicine životnog stila.

908
00:41:00,940 --> 00:41:02,120
 Jer su pametni ljudi shvatili

909
00:41:02,120 --> 00:41:04,840
 da zahvatam u životnom stilu,

910
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:07,040
 možeš pomoći prvo,

911
00:41:07,040 --> 00:41:09,420
 da je pojavnost tih bolesti manja,

912
00:41:09,420 --> 00:41:11,400
 a drugo, ako su se već pojavile bolesti,

913
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:12,800
 da oblažiš njihove posljedice.

914
00:41:13,800 --> 00:41:15,600
 Kad pričamo o pretilosti,

915
00:41:15,600 --> 00:41:18,860
 kao jednoj od poštosti modernog doba,

916
00:41:18,860 --> 00:41:20,860
 koja je ponekad,

917
00:41:20,860 --> 00:41:22,740
 velikim dijelom,

918
00:41:22,740 --> 00:41:24,560
 sad možemo i o tome diskutirati,

919
00:41:24,560 --> 00:41:26,220
 rezultat našeg životnog stila,

920
00:41:26,220 --> 00:41:29,580
 koliko bi ti ljudi zapravo

921
00:41:29,580 --> 00:41:31,740
 koji žele skinuti određenu tijelesnu masu,

922
00:41:31,740 --> 00:41:33,420
 koliko bi se oni trebali kretati

923
00:41:33,420 --> 00:41:34,740
 u odnosu na ove preporuke,

924
00:41:34,740 --> 00:41:35,600
 sad što si rekao,

925
00:41:35,600 --> 00:41:37,760
 pola sata u tom i tom ritmu,

926
00:41:37,760 --> 00:41:38,500
 u drugoj zoni,

927
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:40,880
 postoji li nešto što bi mogli raditi,

928
00:41:40,880 --> 00:41:42,700
 a da opet nije jako invazivno,

929
00:41:42,700 --> 00:41:43,740
 jako veliki stres,

930
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:45,540
 ili da ne idemo u onom smjeru

931
00:41:45,540 --> 00:41:47,480
 dijeta, odricanja i tako dalje,

932
00:41:47,480 --> 00:41:49,100
 da imamo to opet mršavljanje

933
00:41:49,100 --> 00:41:51,180
 nekako na zdraviji način.

934
00:41:51,180 --> 00:41:52,760
 Pa evo, hodanje je aktivnost

935
00:41:52,760 --> 00:41:53,860
 za koju smo mi stvoreni.

936
00:41:53,860 --> 00:41:55,320
 Naše tijelo je stvoreno da hoda.

937
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:57,960
 Naše tijelo je stvoreno da nosi nešto

938
00:41:57,960 --> 00:41:58,880
 u svojim rukama.

939
00:41:58,880 --> 00:42:00,340
 Mi to danas minimalno radimo.

940
00:42:00,340 --> 00:42:01,900
 Minimalno nosimo neke terete

941
00:42:01,900 --> 00:42:02,760
 i minimalno hodamo.

942
00:42:02,760 --> 00:42:03,900
 Dakle, nošenje je nešto

943
00:42:03,900 --> 00:42:04,860
 što nam je prirodno,

944
00:42:04,860 --> 00:42:07,140
 ali ovo što si pitala,

945
00:42:07,140 --> 00:42:08,180
 pa hodanje je rješenje.

946
00:42:08,180 --> 00:42:09,080
 Jednostavno,

947
00:42:09,080 --> 00:42:12,580
 taj broj koraka može biti prva stvar

948
00:42:12,580 --> 00:42:14,520
 koju bilo koja osoba može popraviti.

949
00:42:14,520 --> 00:42:16,200
 Svi danas imamo neku vrstu

950
00:42:16,200 --> 00:42:17,620
 pametnog sata ili mobitela

951
00:42:17,620 --> 00:42:18,440
 ili aplikacije

952
00:42:18,440 --> 00:42:20,680
 i možeš pratiti broj koraka.

953
00:42:20,680 --> 00:42:22,380
 Ako ti je broj koraka u prosjeku

954
00:42:22,380 --> 00:42:23,420
 5000 dnevno,

955
00:42:23,420 --> 00:42:26,560
 znači da baš i nisi previše aktivan.

956
00:42:26,560 --> 00:42:29,140
 Ako želimo blage promjene,

957
00:42:29,140 --> 00:42:30,080
 onda ćemo dizati,

958
00:42:30,080 --> 00:42:31,420
 svaki tjedan ćemo dizati

959
00:42:31,420 --> 00:42:33,220
 za 10% prosjek broja koraka.

960
00:42:33,220 --> 00:42:35,020
 Pa je to zaista blaga promjena

961
00:42:35,020 --> 00:42:36,840
 koju svatko od nas može napraviti.

962
00:42:36,940 --> 00:42:38,760
 da osobe koje žele napraviti

963
00:42:38,760 --> 00:42:40,400
 stvarno veliku promjenu,

964
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:41,720
 trebalo bi, kao što smo rekli,

965
00:42:41,720 --> 00:42:42,560
 početi polako,

966
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:44,660
 početi sa malim koracima,

967
00:42:44,660 --> 00:42:47,100
 donositi puno malih,

968
00:42:47,100 --> 00:42:50,080
 dosadnih i teških odluka u danu.

969
00:42:50,080 --> 00:42:51,980
 A iako su te odluke male,

970
00:42:51,980 --> 00:42:54,420
 u stvari i lagane,

971
00:42:54,420 --> 00:42:55,500
 u stvari su lagane.

972
00:42:55,500 --> 00:42:57,420
 Čekaj, je li teško hodati pola sata?

973
00:42:57,420 --> 00:42:57,660
 Nije.

974
00:42:57,660 --> 00:42:58,700
 A samo znaš što je problem?

975
00:42:58,700 --> 00:43:00,300
 Još lakše je ne hodati.

976
00:43:00,300 --> 00:43:00,840
 Je.

977
00:43:00,840 --> 00:43:03,020
 Dakle, nije stvar ili nešto teško?

978
00:43:03,020 --> 00:43:04,000
 Nije ništa teško.

979
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:06,020
 A ipak je malo lakše to ne raditi.

980
00:43:06,940 --> 00:43:08,140
 I sad je opet stvar motivacije.

981
00:43:08,140 --> 00:43:10,040
 I naći svoj zašto.

982
00:43:10,040 --> 00:43:11,080
 Svi znamo kako.

983
00:43:11,080 --> 00:43:13,360
 Pa čekaj, šta sam ja sad danas rekao,

984
00:43:13,360 --> 00:43:15,780
 što je novo ili drugačije,

985
00:43:15,780 --> 00:43:17,060
 i što netko ne zna.

986
00:43:17,060 --> 00:43:18,200
 Pa svi to znaju.

987
00:43:18,200 --> 00:43:19,760
 Svi znaju kako.

988
00:43:19,760 --> 00:43:21,600
 A samo što nemamo zašto.

989
00:43:22,180 --> 00:43:24,020
 Ja sebe preispitujem isto svaki dan.

990
00:43:24,020 --> 00:43:25,460
 Imam ja svoje zašto,

991
00:43:25,460 --> 00:43:28,300
 koji su drugačiji za neke segmente mog života.

992
00:43:28,300 --> 00:43:31,160
 Zašto za nešto mi je drugo,

993
00:43:31,160 --> 00:43:32,320
 nego zašto za nešto drugo.

994
00:43:32,320 --> 00:43:34,240
 Ali taj zašto je ključ.

995
00:43:34,240 --> 00:43:36,000
 I taj zašto je ključ motivacije,

996
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:36,580
 vjerojatno.

997
00:43:36,580 --> 00:43:37,500
 Ne znam točno,

998
00:43:37,500 --> 00:43:38,100
 ali vjerojatno je.

999
00:43:38,100 --> 00:43:38,620
 Meni je,

1000
00:43:38,620 --> 00:43:40,700
 kad imam neki cilj za dva tjedna,

1001
00:43:40,700 --> 00:43:42,060
 četiri tjedna ili osam tjedana,

1002
00:43:42,060 --> 00:43:44,040
 kad vidim taj cilj vremenski,

1003
00:43:44,040 --> 00:43:44,700
 onda mi je,

1004
00:43:44,700 --> 00:43:46,120
 to mi daje zašto.

1005
00:43:47,120 --> 00:43:48,680
 A kako, pa svi znamo kako.

1006
00:43:48,680 --> 00:43:51,540
 Znači, hoćeš reći da sve ovo što mi pričamo

1007
00:43:51,540 --> 00:43:52,580
 zapravo pada u vodu

1008
00:43:52,580 --> 00:43:54,400
 ako ljudi se prvo ne postaje pitanje

1009
00:43:54,400 --> 00:43:56,280
 zašto ja to uopće moram raditi.

1010
00:43:56,280 --> 00:43:57,080
 Pa da, točno.

1011
00:43:57,080 --> 00:43:58,920
 Možeš podijeliti neki svoj zašto

1012
00:43:58,920 --> 00:44:00,980
 da čujemo kako to zvuči u praksi.

1013
00:44:00,980 --> 00:44:02,860
 Primjerice, ako ideš trenirati,

1014
00:44:02,860 --> 00:44:03,640
 ne dati se,

1015
00:44:03,640 --> 00:44:06,780
 ideš odraditi neki posao, predavanje,

1016
00:44:06,780 --> 00:44:08,880
 nisi baš inspiriran taj dan.

1017
00:44:08,880 --> 00:44:10,300
 Što te zapravo vodi?

1018
00:44:10,300 --> 00:44:11,580
 Koja je ta tvoja svrha ili spisa?

1019
00:44:11,580 --> 00:44:11,940
 Pa ne znam.

1020
00:44:11,940 --> 00:44:14,440
 Ja sam sebi zadajem neki problem

1021
00:44:14,440 --> 00:44:15,900
 da ga jednostavno moram riješiti.

1022
00:44:15,900 --> 00:44:18,400
 Imam neko predavanje

1023
00:44:18,400 --> 00:44:19,500
 i ljudi me pitaju za temu.

1024
00:44:19,500 --> 00:44:20,800
 Ja im namjerno kažem temu

1025
00:44:20,800 --> 00:44:22,920
 koju još nemam spremno.

1026
00:44:22,920 --> 00:44:24,820
 Da bi sam sebe prisilio

1027
00:44:24,820 --> 00:44:26,200
 da pripremim to,

1028
00:44:26,200 --> 00:44:27,440
 da nešto novo proučim,

1029
00:44:27,440 --> 00:44:29,260
 da izađem iz zone konfora

1030
00:44:29,260 --> 00:44:30,260
 i da nešto,

1031
00:44:30,260 --> 00:44:31,700
 nećemu napredujem.

1032
00:44:31,700 --> 00:44:32,820
 Želim napredujem.

1033
00:44:32,820 --> 00:44:35,020
 A tako sam birao teme za svoje radove.

1034
00:44:35,020 --> 00:44:37,240
 Puno toga sam birao tako

1035
00:44:37,240 --> 00:44:38,720
 da sam sebe prisilim.

1036
00:44:38,720 --> 00:44:40,940
 Jer znam da inače će biti uvijek nešto

1037
00:44:40,940 --> 00:44:42,360
 što je interesantnije u tom trenutku.

1038
00:44:42,960 --> 00:44:44,320
 Tako da pokušavam se tako

1039
00:44:44,320 --> 00:44:46,760
 recimo motivirati na takav način.

1040
00:44:46,760 --> 00:44:47,920
 Ili imam za dva tjedna

1041
00:44:47,920 --> 00:44:49,360
 ili četiri tjedna nekakav događaj.

1042
00:44:49,360 --> 00:44:51,060
 Nešto želim zbog tog događaja

1043
00:44:51,060 --> 00:44:52,660
 biti odmorni,

1044
00:44:52,660 --> 00:44:53,860
 biti u boljoj formi,

1045
00:44:53,860 --> 00:44:55,600
 biti i tako dalje.

1046
00:44:55,600 --> 00:44:57,720
 Tako da ti zašto se mijenjaju.

1047
00:44:57,720 --> 00:44:59,960
 A nekad sam sebi zadam

1048
00:44:59,960 --> 00:45:02,560
 nekakav tamo cilj i izazov

1049
00:45:02,560 --> 00:45:05,320
 i onda sam odgovoran prema nekom drugom.

1050
00:45:05,320 --> 00:45:07,580
 A to je najčešće dobar zašto.

1051
00:45:07,580 --> 00:45:09,640
 Nekad sam odgovoran prema svoje djeci.

1052
00:45:09,640 --> 00:45:11,220
 Pa spaj, to je moj zašto.

1053
00:45:11,220 --> 00:45:12,160
 Oni su moji zašto.

1054
00:45:12,160 --> 00:45:13,980
 Pa i zbog njih donosim neke odluke

1055
00:45:13,980 --> 00:45:16,320
 jer želim biti sposoban

1056
00:45:16,320 --> 00:45:18,860
 njihovu djecu hendlati i pomagati njima

1057
00:45:18,860 --> 00:45:21,700
 i biti sposoban nositi unoka.

1058
00:45:21,700 --> 00:45:23,340
 Pa to je dobar zašto.

1059
00:45:23,340 --> 00:45:25,080
 I to je ozbiljan zašto.

1060
00:45:26,020 --> 00:45:29,360
 biti tu za doživjeti pravnuke.

1061
00:45:29,360 --> 00:45:30,960
 To je ozbiljan zašto.

1062
00:45:30,960 --> 00:45:32,380
 E sad ne razmišljamo

1063
00:45:32,380 --> 00:45:33,680
 i ne sjetimo se toga svaki dan.

1064
00:45:33,680 --> 00:45:37,220
 Toga se sjetimo dva puta godišnje.

1065
00:45:37,220 --> 00:45:39,220
 Možda na jednom na sahrani,

1066
00:45:39,220 --> 00:45:40,380
 jedno i drugi put

1067
00:45:40,380 --> 00:45:42,820
 kad gledamo neki film na tu temu.

1068
00:45:42,820 --> 00:45:45,040
 Ali realno to je,

1069
00:45:45,040 --> 00:45:46,080
 nema dalje od toga.

1070
00:45:46,080 --> 00:45:48,820
 To je zašto koji je univerzalan.

1071
00:45:48,820 --> 00:45:50,900
 Samo da ga se sjetimo dovoljno često.

1072
00:45:50,900 --> 00:45:53,380
 I možemo zapisati možda te stvari.

1073
00:45:53,380 --> 00:45:55,240
 Imaš li praksu neka zapisivanja

1074
00:45:55,240 --> 00:45:57,320
 nekih svojih misli, ideja,

1075
00:45:57,320 --> 00:45:59,160
 svog zašto, svog cilja?

1076
00:45:59,160 --> 00:46:01,040
 Pa neke ciljeve zapisujem, da.

1077
00:46:01,040 --> 00:46:03,260
 Pa ciljeve zapisujem

1078
00:46:03,260 --> 00:46:04,460
 i to možda ne često.

1079
00:46:04,460 --> 00:46:06,640
 Možda i namirno ne često.

1080
00:46:06,640 --> 00:46:07,940
 Jer želim si dat vrijeme

1081
00:46:07,940 --> 00:46:09,580
 da ih ostvarim.

1082
00:46:09,580 --> 00:46:10,820
 Neke ih zaboravim.

1083
00:46:10,820 --> 00:46:12,360
 Pa poste vidim da sam zapisao.

1084
00:46:12,360 --> 00:46:13,360
 Pa sam neke ostvario,

1085
00:46:13,360 --> 00:46:14,040
 neke nisam.

1086
00:46:14,040 --> 00:46:15,800
 Ciljevi koji se zadajem

1087
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:17,000
 su obično dosta visoki.

1088
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:19,220
 Jer i tak ih neću ostvariti.

1089
00:46:19,220 --> 00:46:20,900
 Pa ako već neću ostvariti,

1090
00:46:20,900 --> 00:46:21,800
