1224
00:50:32,200 --> 00:50:33,560
 koji su jako talentirani

1225
00:50:33,560 --> 00:50:34,980
 zbog toga su tu di jesu.

1226
00:50:34,980 --> 00:50:36,320
 No evo,

1227
00:50:36,320 --> 00:50:38,160
