1231
00:50:42,660 --> 00:50:44,160
 Spominješ organizaciju,

1232
00:50:44,160 --> 00:50:45,260
 odmicanje od ega,

1233
00:50:45,260 --> 00:50:47,000
 kompetitivnost,

