1280
00:51:57,340 --> 00:51:58,780
 trošiti nepotrebno.

1281
00:51:58,780 --> 00:51:59,700
 Dakle, ekonomičan si

1282
00:51:59,700 --> 00:52:00,440
 u svemu što radiš,

